<font color="#FF0000">VIETNAM IN MY LIFE</font><br>
<tt>Thu Dec  5  8:03:27 US/Eastern 1996
</tt><p>
While not exactly post war - I am - Vietnam has prevaded my life in so many areas!<br><br>
My father was killed in the Republic of Vietnam in 1968 while serving in the US military - He was killed by a B40 rocket.<br><br>
I was married to A vietnam Veteran who has been both hospitalized and institutionalized since we divorced 14 years ago because of PTSD, drug and alcohol abuse.<br><br>
I have been working with Vietnam Veterans and their families for the past 6 years through the Friends of the Vietnam Veterans Memorial.  I help connect the family, friends and fellow veterans of those killed or missing in Vietnam.  <br><br>
I am one of the three incorporators of an organization for the children of those lost in Vietnam.  Sons and Daughters In Touch.  <br><br>
I am in love with and engaged to a disabled Vietnam Veteran. 
